### 📎 Upload Treatment Certificate Documents

Please upload the treatment certificate and any related documents for the consignment.

* **Reference Number**: `{{.reference_number}}`
* **Treatment Provider**: {{if eq .treatment_provider "npqs"}}NPQS Treatment Division{{else}}Registered Private Treatment Provider{{end}}
* **Supervision**: {{if eq .treatment_supervision "with_supervision"}}With supervision — please also upload the supervision report{{else}}Without supervision{{end}}

**Required Documents:**
* Treatment Certificate (from NPQS or registered provider)
{{if eq .treatment_supervision "with_supervision"}}* Supervision Report (from the PQS/NPQS supervising officer){{end}}

Once submitted, an NPQS officer will review the uploaded documents.
